An userscript that shows Chinese input method hint in typeracer.com. 
Hint is shown when you type the wrong word.
Right now only Cangjie is supported (both version 3 and 5).

Tested on Firefox 8.0.1

Need to install Greasemonkey in Firefox:
https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/greasemonkey/

To install the script, click:
https://github.com/ypcat/typeracer_hint/raw/master/typeracer.user.js

To run the script, visit:
http://play.typeracer.com/?universe=lang_zh-tw

